  "npcs": [
    {
      "name": "Courage",
      "x": 2,
      "y": 14,
      "sprite": "Monster",
      "sprite_index": 2,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "right",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Courage",
        "portrait": "Monster",
        "face_index": 2,
        "lines": [
          "I committed a buffer overflow fix right before Evie rang the bell. I still have the cognitive zoomies so I'm going to write some Rust!",
          "It's a full moon, the sky is clear, and I love coding. Awooooooo!"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Ocean",
      "x": 20,
      "y": 9,
      "sprite": "People4",
      "sprite_index": 0,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Ocean",
        "portrait": "People4",
        "face_index": 0,
        "lines": [
          "I'm not the best programmer and Luna's not the best tester. As a pair we kick butt.",
          "It's almost as if we and the computers and the code all become one in the simulation.",
          "Heh, sorry. I don't know if it's the cybernetics papers or Trek fics that make me like this."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Nyaanager Evie",
      "x": 12,
      "y": 8,
      "sprite": "Nature",
      "sprite_index": 4,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Nyaanager Evie",
        "portrait": "Nature",
        "face_index": 4,
        "lines": [
          "We had a tricky incident today so I took the pager and told my team to scram.",
          "I love my team and they totally rock. I do my best to protect them but the pressure from Mahogany Row is getting to me.",
          "I can't get promoted without driving my team harder and I know in my toebeans that it would halt their growth."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Seventh Daughter of Nine",
      "x": 20,
      "y": 13,
      "sprite": "People2",
      "sprite_index": 5,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "left",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Seventh Daughter of Nine",
        "portrait": "People2",
        "face_index": 5,
        "lines": [
          "Oh yeah, we had an incident. I only know the gist of it right now. We'll do interviews next week after the team has processed a bit.",
          "Xela was bragging about the error budget so we're comparing it to the timeline to incident estimate customer impact."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Luna",
      "x": 7,
      "y": 14,
      "sprite": "People2",
      "sprite_index": 1,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "left",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Luna",
        "portrait": "People2",
        "face_index": 1,
        "lines": [
          "I paired with my bestie, Ocean today. I used to be skeptical about pairing and now I'm one of THOSE PEOPLE.",
          "Nyaanager and Ocean were so paitent with me while I got the hang of it. I look forward to it now."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Doctor Mcfire",
      "x": 3,
      "y": 5,
      "sprite": "DrMcfire",
      "sprite_index": 0,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Doctor McFire",
        "portrait": "DrMcfire",
        "face_index": 0,
        "lines": [
          "On-call is such a rush. One minute you're typing away and the next you're the incident commander.",
          "When I went from the SLO alert to traces I immediately knew I screwed up. Rolling forward was just as easy as rollback so I cut a pull request.",
          "Some people complain but I love incidents. I should write a paper about them, that would be cool."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Hidaslo Xela",
      "x": 18,
      "y": 13,
      "sprite": "People3",
      "sprite_index": 6,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "right",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Hidaslo Xela",
        "portrait": "People3",
        "face_index": 6,
        "lines": [
          "I know I'm not supposed to gloat but the error budget alert was the first to fire and we were on it before customers noticed.",
          "Nobody else is doing SLOs yet. I believe SLOs will help the Disco push back on Mahogany Row and keep Inferno honest."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Boba Jacobian",
      "x": 14,
      "y": 14,
      "sprite": "Mando",
      "sprite_index": 0,
      "step_anime": false,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Boba Jacobian",
        "portrait": "casey",
        "face_index": 4,
        "lines": [
          "Nyaanager runs a Westrum generative team. She doesn't call it that though. This is the way."
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
